OL,3,CMolly-Mae and Tommy Fury welcome
OL,4,Csecond child
OL,6,FSocial media star Molly-Mae Hague and
OL,7,Fboxer Tommy Fury have welcomed their
OL,8,Fsecond child.
OL,10,FThe couple, who met on the ITV dating
OL,11,Fshow Love Island, had their first
OL,12,Fdaughter Bambi in January 2023 with
OL,13,FHague announcing she was pregnant with
OL,14,Ftheir second child in February this
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FOn Wednesday, 3 June, the pair
OL,18,Frevealed the news in a joint Instagram
OL,19,Fpost which featured the trio admiring
OL,20,Fthe new member of their family in a
OL,21,Fblack and white photograph.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
