OL,3,CMolly-Mae and Tommy Fury welcome
OL,4,Csecond child
OL,6,FThe caption read: "...and then there
OL,7,Fwere 4."
OL,9,FThe post received more than 1.5
OL,10,Fmillion likes within the first two
OL,11,Fhours of being shared online with
OL,12,Ffriends and fans celebrating the news
OL,13,Fin the comments section.
OL,15,FAmong them was TV host and former Love
OL,16,FIslander, Maura Higgins, who said:
OL,17,F"Congratulations again. So happy for
OL,18,Fyou all."
