OL,3,CMolly-Mae and Tommy Fury welcome
OL,4,Csecond child
OL,6,FHague and Fury met in 2019 on the
OL,7,Ffifth series of Love Island where they
OL,8,Ffinished in second place.
OL,10,FAfter the show they remained together
OL,11,Fand were engaged to one another until
OL,12,Fthey split up in August 2024.
OL,14,FThe pair rekindled their relationship
OL,15,Fand confirmed they were back together
OL,16,Fin May last year.
OL,18,FSince being on Love Island, Hague has
OL,19,Famassed 8.6 million Instagram
OL,20,Ffollowers and in 2024 launched her own
OL,21,Fclothing brand, Maebe.
